      233.72,
      558.08,
      300.96
    ],
    "text": "The low-pressure area located northeast of the Sri Lanka, still persist. Under the influence of this system, wind speed and rainy conditions over the sea areas around the island may increase. The naval and fishing communities are requested to be attentive to the future forecasts and bulletins issued by the Department of Meteorology in this regard.",
