  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      61.34,
      336.76,
      558.1,
      381.72
    ],
    "text": "Showers or thundershowers will occur at times in the sea areas off the coast extending from Mullaittivu to Galle via Kankasanthurai, Puttalam and Colombo. Showers or thundershowers will occur at several places elsewhere around the island in the evening or night.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      61.34,
      390.28,
      558.1,
      467.76
    ],
    "text": "Winds: Winds will be southwesterly. Wind speed will be (25-35) kmph. Wind speed can increase up to (50-55) kmph at times in the sea areas off the coast extending from Kankasanthurai to Pottuvil via Puttalam, Colombo, Galle and Hambantota. State of Sea:",
